{"id": 4712, "title": "Ticket #4712: Fix shared_port with mixed-mode IPv4/IPv6", "description": "<blockquote>\nCurrent challenges:\n<ul>\n<li>Looks like condor_shared_port may bind to different ports on IPv4 and IPv6.  It should always bind to a singular port on all protocols. (It's the shared port, not shared ports.)\n</li><li>Rewrite code may not be able to cope with shared ports at all.\n</li></ul>\n\n<p>This is a successor to <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=4494\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('4494'); return false;\" title=\"IPv6: mixed-mode submit node (schedd/shadow)\">#4494</a></span>: IPv6: mixed-mode submit node (schedd/shadow)\n\n</p><p><span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=4635\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('4635'); return false;\" title=\"The CMS IPv6 Requirements and Problems\">#4635</a></span>: The CMS IPv6 Requirements and Problems relies on this.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<em>2014-Dec-02 10:24:28 by tlmiller:</em> <br/>\n\nNeeds to be merged.</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2015-Feb-18 13:43</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/239b3e44a562ab6ae08abe883280250b2c00983d\">[43397]</a></span>: edit version history item for <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=4712\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('4712'); return false;\" title=\"Fix shared_port with mixed-mode IPv4/IPv6\">#4712</a></span>  (By Karen Miller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2015-Feb-17 14:3